{"tid":1583463,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone版，去左呢頁點出番去","createTime":"2019-09-20T15:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T15:36:40.000Z","uid":172349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff09129f8dbc2108efbfc50ffbd381b820b45802","tid":1583463,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無得出番去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QK3cNOg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQK3cNOg.jpg&h=4409f691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cecec7d0eae31786f8da0089ba74933f02616032","tid":1583463,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span></span>借減碳排放為名，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要向中國買電</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"0da46225cff065b47f307ea5be1a2d4a80545158","tid":1583463,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:16:55.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG169osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=af3da62b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"bcfc8fb6fb631e76270b0772168ef6c10ce2b727","tid":1583463,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"買過部機"},{"pid":"2c50b0824b68007740d3c1f7d0cc172710ed85e4","tid":1583463,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrkZsS0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrkZsS0.png&h=c53de367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上角㩒帳號"},{"pid":"deeea7a9e170e9733a92b1a217733dc0297b8704","tid":1583463,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c50b0824b68007740d3c1f7d0cc172710ed85e4","tid":1583463,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrkZsS0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrkZsS0.p